root: ^: A black sedan parked in front of your apartment complex is alarming; its windshield is shattered.
^ Across the street, a man burns down a convenience store, the fire shooting from his bare hands.
^ His partner carries two heavy metal safes that were ripped from the walls of the store.
^[NAME]: (Wait… what? “Just another day,” but this isn’t… normal, is it?)
^[NAME]: (This shouldn’t be happening, the world shouldn’t be… Why is everything… )
